            <div class="title">
                Mutiny Charges, Malaya (Convictions Quashed)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1946-10-10/debates/6531e6e7-02e2-4548-a717-73059b19343f/HousingScotland" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span>
